{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/Battles.gif?t=1736553421\" /><br>Defend your shrine against humanity as the last, and oh-so-vengeful god in this turn-based roguelike strategy game. Each run presents new challenges and opportunities to expand your reservoir of spells and summons against the blasphemous mortals who slaughtered every god in existence\u2026 except you. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/ENG-Turn_Based.png?t=1736553421\" /><br>Each turn, manage your resources to turn the tides of randomly-generated battles in your favor and protect your shrine at all costs.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Will you summon <strong>auto-battling units</strong> that attack, buff, or heal?<br></li><li>Will you <strong>cast spells</strong> to resurrect, enchant or poison targets?<br></li><li>Will you <strong>terraform the map</strong> with tiles that boost, block or teleport units? </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/ENG-Endless_Synergies.png?t=1736553421\" /><br>Between battles, choose your path and upgrades wisely to find the optimal synergetic build for your next fight. Discover hundreds of items in four different elemental classes to create unique builds each run!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/Endless-Tactical-Synergies.gif?t=1736553421\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/ENG-Powerful_Progression.png?t=1736553421\" /><br>Unlock permanent upgrades after each run to destroy the ten continents and decide the fate of the world!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/Ru